## ğŸ§  Tech Stack  

- **Frontend**: [Next.js](https://nextjs.org/) + [TypeScript](https://www.typescriptlang.org/)  
- **Backend**: [Node.js](https://nodejs.org/) + [Express.js](https://expressjs.com/)  
- **Database**: [Supabase](https://supabase.io/) â€“ HIPAA-compliant PostgreSQL  
- **Authentication**: Supabase Auth / Firebase Auth  
- **Video Calls**: [WebRTC](https://webrtc.org/) / [Twilio](https://www.twilio.com/) / [Agora](https://www.agora.io/)  
- **Payments**: [Stripe](https://stripe.com/) / [PayPal](https://paypal.com)  
- **Hosting**: [Vercel](https://vercel.com/) / AWS  

